column5: Went out on Monday for some bass on Rice and had a good day as I was able to boat a few nice bass and one nice smallmouth with some nice spots..  As well I've been out on the Ganny for the salmon run.. check out da pic's
Nice catches! Keep up the good work!
Very nice. Looking forward to hitting rice soon!
Beauties    Great job  flyguy5 Thanks for sharing Leechman
Nice fish you got there. I am getting cabin fever, got to get out fishing!!!  Take Care, Mike

Nice fish! I fish Rice Lake this season every weekend but find the smallmouth bite very sporadic. May be just one or two occasionally at a spot. Too far and few in between. So I mostly target largemouth. At least I know where the weeds are...
